wearables.name: Aastronaut Crew Member
wearables.description: This baadge signifies that this is one of the original five Aavegotchis to be bridged from Polygon to Ethereum. Dubbed the "Aastronauts" these pioneering gotchis were fractionalized on the Unicly platform in the form of uGOTCHI tokens. In October of 2021 the uGOTCHI collection was unlocked and all five Aastronauts were auctioned to new owners.
wearables.author: xibot

wearables.name: CHAAMPION of Rarity Farming SZN2 (Rarity)
wearables.description: Scored across all four rounds, this Aavegotchi is the ultimate chaampion of rarity for Rarity Farming SZN 2. Aamazing! From October 12 to Dec 7, 2021, the second season of Rarity Farming distributed a staggering 2 million GHST. The frenly competition featured three main leaderboards that any summoned Aavegotchi could participate in plus two additional Rookie Leaderboards for Haunt 2 Aavegotchis.
wearables.author: xibot
